<th class="tableblock halign-left valign-top">Explanation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>PAYMENT.SALE.COMPLETED</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">A payment has been completed. When PayPal sends this notification, a pending payment is marked as paid in plentymarkets.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>PAYMENT.SALE.DENIED</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">A payment has been denied. When PayPal sends this notification, a pending payment is marked as unpaid in plentymarkets.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>PAYMENT.SALE.PENDING</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">There is a pending payment. When PayPal sends this notification, a pending payment is created in plentymarkets.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
