<h2 id="70">6. Activating the payment method</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Activate the payment method once in your system. Note that only the activation of the payment method is needed. All other settings, for example for clients or delivery countries, don’t have any effects.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Activation of payment method:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Orders » Payment » Methods</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the payment methods you want to activate.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the <strong>Active</strong> option (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-check-square  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
